639
00:40:10.760 --> 00:40:13.300
Non ha niente! 
Lascialo stare!

640
00:40:13.380 --> 00:40:14.380
Basta!

641
00:40:15.550 --> 00:40:18.260
- Rav!
- Dov'è la Fenice?


642
00:40:18.970 --> 00:40:19.970
Tom!

643
00:40:20.770 --> 00:40:21.770
Tom!

644
00:40:22.390 --> 00:40:26.940
